    <p>    Christoffel Jegher (Flemish, 1596-1652/53)<br />
after Peter Paul Rubens (Flemish, 1577-1640)<br />
    </p>
    <h3><em>The Temptation of Christ by the Devil</em>, 1633/35</h3>

    <p>
    Woodcut in black on cream laid paper, tipped onto ivory laid paper mount prepared with ochre wash<br />    324 x 432 (image); 336 x 444 mm (page); 390 x 497 mm (secondary support)<br />        Amanda S. Johnson and Marion J. Livingston Endowment, 1998.362</p>
    <p>Schneevoogt N. Test. 138; Hollstein vol. IX, 6 II</p>    
        <!--<p id="dept-gallery">--><!--<br />-->
         <!--</p>-->
    </p>
